		chemistry ,4 th ed .Prentice -Hall International , Inc.

 

2.Robert M. Silverstein ,Francis 
		X ., Webster. Spectrometric Identification of OrganicCompounds,6th ed 
		.John Wiley ＆ 
		Son, Inc .

 

3.Douglas A . Skoog , F. James 
		Holler Timothy A . Nieman  . Principles of Instrumental Analysis ,4 th 
